<subSubSection id="CBC06566FFB8FF9964BAFC4BFD41FBE8" pageId="8" pageNumber="225" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="836536EDFFB8FF9964BAFC4BFD41FBE8" blockId="8.[151,1127,916,1163]" pageId="8" pageNumber="225">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB8FF9964BAFC4BFEDDFC08" bold="true" box="[151,268,916,939]" pageId="8" pageNumber="225">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB8FF9965AAFC4BFE2EFC08" authorityName="Koch" authorityYear="1941" box="[391,511,916,939]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Indochillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="225" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB8FF9965AAFC4BFE2EFC08" box="[391,511,916,939]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="225">Indochillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is characterized by prominent suborbital keel. Eyes completely divided by genae. Clypeus concave, with one small tooth in middle. Tempora concave. Occiput with sharply bordered triangular impression with mid-longitudinal keel. Base of elytra markedly wider than pronotal base. Elytra with keeled intervals 3, 5, 7 and 9, interval 3 and 5 flattened behind first quarter of its length, interval 5 keeled also in its last (apical) fifth. Antennomere 3 as long as antennomere 4.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="CBC06566FFB8FF9964BAFB8BFCAFFB28" pageId="8" pageNumber="225" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="836536EDFFB8FF9964BAFB8BFCAFFB28" blockId="8.[151,1127,916,1163]" pageId="8" pageNumber="225">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB8FF9964BAFB8BFED7FBC8" bold="true" box="[151,262,1108,1131]" pageId="8" pageNumber="225">Remarks.</emphasis>
This genus does not belong to the fauna of South 
<collectingCountry id="FBCD767DFFB8FF996705FB8BFC40FBC8" box="[808,913,1108,1131]" name="China" pageId="8" pageNumber="225">East Asia</collectingCountry>
, but it is mentioned here because of its close relation to the genus 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB8FF9966ACFBABFCC6FB28" authority="Fouquè, 2015" authorityName="Fouquè" authorityYear="2015" box="[641,791,1140,1163]" genus="Pseudochillus" pageId="8" pageNumber="225" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB8FF9966ACFBABFCC6FB28" box="[641,791,1140,1163]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="225">Pseudochillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="AA9D5784FFB8FF996730FBABFCAFFB28" box="[797,894,1140,1163]" pageId="8" pageNumber="225" rank="genus">gen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
